  <statement>
      
      
      <p>
          Suppose you had a class of  <m>27</m>  children.
      </p>
      
      
      <p>
          <ol>
              <li>How many ways are there to select <m>4</m>  children  and arrange them so they can take turns giving a presentation?</li>
              <li>How many ways are there to select <m>23</m>  children  and put them in a line to wait their turn for an activity?</li>
              <li>How many ways are there to select <m>14</m>  children  to give a special assignment?</li>
              <li>How many ways are there to select <m>15</m>  children  to take on a field trip?</li>
          </ol>
          
      </p>
      
      
     
      
          
          
          
          
      
  </statement>
